Title: www.ncert.nic.in Computer Typist  

Recruitment

www.ncert.nic.in - National Council of Educational Research and Training  

released employment notification. It invites applications from eligible
and  
competent candidates for walk-in-interview for the recruitment to the post
 
of Computer Typist vacancy on temporary basis. This is only a shortened  
version of the original employment news notification with some important  

details. Read on...
